> >
> > I had a tough problem getting the passenger side cover off my bus.  The trick
> > for me was to use a 2x4 and a rubber mallet to knock it off.  Put the 2x4
> > lengthwise against the bottom of the cover and give it several knocks with the
> > rubber mallet.
> >
> > -Pete
